  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the efficacy, safety, tolerability of imatinib in the neoadjuvant
      treatment (pre-operatory) of patients with GIST. It will also evaluate the potential of
      imatinib to convert a tumor from inoperable to operable.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
